<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="興福" xml:id="gsz0885a14shiShiHui"><lb
ed="T" n="0885a14"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0885a14"/><head><date from-iso="+0947-03-15" key="j20670182068464" to-iso="+0951-02-28">漢</date>東京天壽禪院<persName key="A013789">師會</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0885a15"/><persName key="A013789">釋師會</persName>，俗姓巨，漢<placeName key="PL000000027770">荊州</placeName>刺史<persName key="A013790">武</persName>之後，祖徙家<lb
ed="T" n="0885a16"/><placeName key="PL000000000514">北燕</placeName>，遂為<placeName key="PL000000000369">薊門</placeName>人也。考諱<persName key="A019509">知古</persName>，母<persName key="A019510">趙<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>。<persName key="A013789">會</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0885a17"/>童孩出俗，禮薊州<placeName key="PL000000000757">溫泉院</placeName><persName key="A011683">道丕</persName>為師匠焉。<lb
ed="T" n="0885a18"/>業成，年滿，受具於金臺<placeName key="PL000000000358">寶剎寺</placeName>壇。<date key="j20524952053950" notAfter-iso="+0911-06-04" notBefore-iso="+0907-06-10">梁<name>開平</name>中</date><lb
ed="T" n="0885a19"/>萍梗任飄於<placeName key="PL000000000084">河朔</placeName>，杯盂隨步於<placeName key="PL000000015039">江淮</placeName>，乃抵<lb
ed="T" n="0885a20"/><placeName key="PL000000027770">漢南</placeName>遇觀音院<persName key="A013791">巖俊</persName>，班荊<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1635"/>話道，抵掌論心。<lb
ed="T" n="0885a21"/>且曰：「子還聞<placeName key="PL000000015565">投子山</placeName>有<persName key="A009447">大同禪師</persName>已否？」曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0885a22"/>「聞而未見。」曰：「宜亟往焉。」及參<persName key="A009447">大同</persName>，跬步之<lb
ed="T" n="0885a23"/><anchor xml:id="beg0885sgsz1"/>間<anchor xml:id="end0885sgsz1"/>，舉揚之外，洗焉明白，其安坦然。<date key="j20541872054363" notAfter-iso="+0912-07-21" notBefore-iso="+0912-01-27"><name>乾化</name>二年</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0885a24"/>來<placeName key="PL000000023340">梁苑</placeName>，謝<persName key="A013791">俊公</persName>曰：「始者攸攸<anchor xml:id="beg0885sgsz3"/>岐<anchor xml:id="end0885sgsz3"/>路，茫茫生<lb
ed="T" n="0885a25"/>死，紫實昧朱，狂斯濫哲。苟不奉師友指歸，<lb
ed="T" n="0885a26"/>幾一生空度。今以穢蕕，請與薰同器而藏，<lb
ed="T" n="0885a27"/>可乎？」<persName key="A013791">俊公</persName>與<persName key="A013789">會</persName>胥德，留入法席。<date key="j20549252055278" notAfter-iso="+0915-01-22" notBefore-iso="+0914-02-03">四年</date>秋，有<lb
ed="T" n="0885a28"/>寶積坊羅漢院<!--找不到此地--><persName key="A013792">志修</persName>堅請<persName key="A013789">會</persName>代居所住焉，<lb
ed="T" n="0885a29"/>苫蓋五<anchor xml:id="beg0885sgsz5"/>間<anchor xml:id="end0885sgsz5"/>而已。乃感檀越尚書左丞<persName key="A013793">吳藹</persName>、兵<pb ed="T" n="0885b" xml:id="T50.2061.0885b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0885b01"/>部侍郎<persName key="A013794">張袞</persName>，若<persName key="A002985">袁粲</persName>之謁<persName key="A001921">寶亮</persName>，<persName key="A002991">徐湛之</persName>禮<lb
ed="T" n="0885b02"/><persName key="A013795">惠通</persName>，共發奉章，賜額曰<placeName key="PL000000023316">天壽</placeName>焉。四海之僧，<lb
ed="T" n="0885b03"/>翕然<ptr type="glossary" target="#g768"/>而至。歷三十五載，供僧二百餘萬，用<lb
ed="T" n="0885b04"/>其財寶，無少混淆，耿介可知也。<date key="j20651432065331" notAfter-iso="+0942-08-01" notBefore-iso="+0942-01-25"><name>天福</name>七年</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0885b05"/><persName key="A006579">晉高祖</persName>以<persName key="A013789">會</persName>行成于內，聲聞於外，勅賜紫<lb
ed="T" n="0885b06"/>衣。<date key="j20660582066264" notAfter-iso="+0945-02-19" notBefore-iso="+0944-07-28"><name>開運</name>元年</date>，賜號曰<persName key="A013789">法相</persName>。紫衣則藏以受<lb
ed="T" n="0885b07"/>持，師號則蔑其稱謂。且曰：「<persName key="A013789">我</persName>本不求名，名<lb
ed="T" n="0885b08"/>來自求<persName key="A013789">我</persName>。知其白而守其黑，和其光而同<lb
ed="T" n="0885b09"/>其塵，世幻逡巡，時不<persName key="A013789">我</persName>與。」<date key="j20668212066821" when-iso="0946">三年七月二十六<lb
ed="T" n="0885b10"/>日</date>累諸門人，帖然而滅，春秋六十七，夏臘<lb
ed="T" n="0885b11"/>四十八。闍維，收舍利數百粒，起塔於東郊<placeName key="PL000000023303">汴<lb
ed="T" n="0885b12"/>陽鄉</placeName>也。刑部侍郎<persName key="A013796">邊歸讜</persName>為碑頌德云。</p>
